{"slug":"when-a-man-s-in-love","title":{"en":"When a Man's in Love","km":"ធ្លាក់ក្នុងអន្លង់ស្នេហ៍អូន"},"description":{"en":"Han Tae Sang (Song Seung Heon) is a cold-blooded businessman who rose from a destitute childhood to achieve immense wealth and power through sheer, ruthless determination. Haunted by the traumas of his youth, he lives a life devoid of warmth or affection. However, his frozen world begins to melt when he meets Seo Mi Do (Shin Se Kyung), a spirited, ambitious young woman whose struggles to escape poverty strongly mirror his own past. For the first time in his life, Tae Sang experiences the vulnerability of love.\n\nYet, their burgeoning relationship is threatened by deep socio-economic divides, past secrets, and a fierce rivalry when Lee Jae Hee (Yeon Woo Jin), a bright and charming young man, falls for Mi Do as well. Drawn into a passionate yet dangerous love triangle, Tae Sang must navigate intense betrayal and determine if his love can survive the dark realities of his world.","km":"ហាន\u200B ថេសាង\u200B (Han\u200B Tae\u200B Sang)\u200B គឺជា\u200Bសហគ្រិន\u200Bឈាម\u200Bត្រជាក់\u200Bម្នាក់\u200B ដែល\u200Bបាន\u200Bតស៊ូ\u200Bរំដោះ\u200Bខ្លួន\u200Bចេញ\u200Bពី\u200Bភាព\u200Bក្រីក្រ\u200Bតោកយ៉ាក\u200Bក្នុង\u200Bកុមារភាព\u200B រហូត\u200Bទទួល\u200Bបាន\u200Bទ្រព្យសម្បត្តិ\u200B និង\u200Bអំណាច\u200Bយ៉ាង\u200Bមហិមា\u200B តាម\u200Bរយៈ\u200Bការ\u200Bសម្រេច\u200Bចិត្ត\u200Bដ៏\u200Bម៉ឺងម៉ាត់\u200B និង\u200Bគ្មាន\u200Bមេត្តា\u200B។\u200B ដោយ\u200Bសារ\u200Bតែ\u200Bរបួស\u200Bផ្លូវ\u200Bចិត្ត\u200Bកាល\u200Bពី\u200Bយុវវ័យ\u200B គាត់\u200Bបាន\u200Bរស់\u200Bនៅ\u200Bក្នុង\u200Bជីវិត\u200Bមួយ\u200Bដែល\u200Bគ្មាន\u200Bភាព\u200Bកក់ក្តៅ\u200B ឬ\u200Bក្តី\u200Bស្រឡាញ់\u200Bឡើយ\u200B។\u200B ទោះ\u200Bជា\u200Bយ៉ាង\u200Bណា\u200B ពិភពលោក\u200Bដ៏\u200Bត្រជាក់\u200Bស្រទុំ\u200Bរបស់\u200Bគាត់\u200Bបាន\u200Bចាប់\u200Bផ្តើម\u200Bរលាយ\u200B នៅ\u200Bពេល\u200Bដែល\u200Bគាត់\u200Bបាន\u200Bជួប\u200Bនឹង\u200B ស៊ូ\u200B មីឌូ\u200B (Seo\u200B Mi\u200B Do)\u200B ដែល\u200Bជា\u200Bនារី\u200Bវ័យ\u200Bក្មេង\u200Bម្នាក់\u200Bប្រកប\u200Bដោយ\u200Bមហិច្ឆតា\u200B និង\u200Bការ\u200Bតស៊ូ\u200B ហើយ\u200Bជីវិត\u200Bតស៊ូ\u200Bប្រឆាំង\u200Bនឹង\u200Bវាសនា\u200Bរបស់\u200Bនាង\u200B បាន\u200Bរំឭក\u200Bគាត់\u200Bអំពី\u200Bអតីតកាល\u200Bរបស់\u200Bខ្លួន\u200Bឯង\u200B។\u200B ជា\u200Bលើក\u200Bដំបូង\u200Bក្នុង\u200Bជីវិត\u200Bរបស់\u200B ថេសាង\u200B ដែល\u200Bគាត់\u200Bបាន\u200Bស្គាល់\u200Bនូវ\u200Bរសជាតិ\u200Bនៃ\u200Bក្តី\u200Bស្រឡាញ់\u200Bពិត\u200Bប្រាកដ\u200B។\n\nទោះ\u200Bជា\u200Bយ៉ាង\u200Bណា\u200B ទំនាក់ទំនង\u200Bដែល\u200Bទើប\u200Bតែ\u200Bចាប់\u200Bផ្តើម\u200Bរបស់\u200Bពួកគេ\u200B ត្រូវ\u200Bបាន\u200Bគំរាម\u200Bកំហែង\u200Bដោយ\u200Bគម្លាត\u200Bសង្គម\u200Bដ៏\u200Bជ្រាលជ្រៅ\u200B អាថ៌កំបាំង\u200Bពី\u200Bអតីតកាល\u200B និង\u200Bការ\u200Bប្រជែង\u200Bគ្នា\u200Bដ៏\u200Bស្រួចស្រាវ\u200B នៅ\u200Bពេល\u200Bដែល\u200B លី\u200B ជែហ៊ី\u200B (Lee\u200B Jae\u200B Hee)\u200B ដែល\u200Bជា\u200Bបុរស\u200Bវ័យ\u200Bក្មេង\u200Bដ៏\u200Bមាន\u200Bមន្តស្នេហ៍\u200Bម្នាក់\u200Bទៀត\u200B ក៏\u200Bបាន\u200Bលង់\u200Bស្នេហ៍\u200B មីឌូ\u200B ផង\u200Bដែរ\u200B។\u200B ដោយ\u200Bធ្លាក់\u200Bចូល\u200Bទៅ\u200Bក្នុង\u200Bទំនាក់ទំនង\u200Bស្នេហា\u200Bត្រីកោណ\u200Bដ៏\u200Bស្មុគ\u200Bស្មាញ\u200B និង\u200Bគ្រោះថ្នាក់\u200Bនេះ\u200B ថេសាង\u200B ត្រូវ\u200Bតែ\u200Bឆ្លង\u200Bកាត់\u200Bការ\u200Bក្បត់\u200Bដ៏\u200Bឈឺ\u200Bចាប់\u200B និង\u200Bស្វែង\u200Bរក\u200Bថា\u200Bតើ\u200Bក្តី\u200Bស្រឡាញ់\u200Bរបស់\u200Bគាត់\u200Bអាច\u200Bយក\u200Bឈ្នះ\u200Bលើ\u200Bការពិត\u200Bដ៏\u200Bខ្មៅ\u200Bងងឹត\u200Bនៃ\u200Bពិភពលោក\u200Bរបស់\u200Bគាត់\u200Bបាន\u200Bដែរ\u200Bឬ\u200Bទេ\u200B។"},"poster":"https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BMjNhOTEwNjItMjA3MS00OWQwLWI0M2ItYjhmMzc3Y2UyNDVkXkEyXkFqcGc@._V1_FMjpg_UX1000_.jpg","year":2013,"rating":6.3,"genres":["ACTION","COMEDY","DRAMA","ROMANCE"],"episodeCount":36,"episodes":[{"ep":"1","title":{"en":"Episode 1","km":"ភាគទី1"},"url":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/ipro855/am/refs/heads/f1/x/index.single","type":"M3U8","final":false},{"ep":"2","title":{"en":"Episode 2","km":"ភាគទី2"},"url":"https://raw.g